{"tid":734452,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】射 Day224 8/7","createTime":"2018-07-08T15:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-08T17:44:23.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1f20af6e195ebe446fbb83e5c2322c387f2cdc","tid":734452,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=CJMkycaNPSOu6GMVJ4Fa2zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=98bf35d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=CJMkycaNPSOu6GMVJ4Fa2zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=23245f21\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"451697b2c606256ce2048f20f3311b8da12981a7","tid":734452,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:39:02.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739cbeb135f675d39180565caf0614eb0406d5bd","tid":734452,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T15:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"319feaecfdc99bca3a79ba2314f07950bb614026","tid":734452,"uid":122942